## Casual prelude and errands  
- Light banter about ‚ÄúJohnny,‚Äù keys, kids logistics

## Vin, Kelsier, and Luthadel setting  
- Ash falls from the sky; oppressive city described  
- Luthadel ruled by lord ruler and ministries  
- Ministry offices feared; Canton of Inquisition notorious  

## Cayman, Vin, and the ministry scam  
- Cayman leads crew, including Vin, to ministry building

## Betrayal of Theron‚Äôs original plan

## Vin‚Äôs reaction and cynicism
